OL,3,CCampaigners fear digital ID scheme
OL,4,Ccould be used as 'weapon of abuse'
OL,6,FITV News reporter Sam Blackledge looks
OL,7,Fat concerns over plans for a digital
OL,8,FID scheme
OL,10,FA domestic abuse campaigner from
OL,11,FPlymouth is urging the Government to
OL,12,Flisten to concerns about plans for a
OL,13,Fdigital ID scheme.
OL,15,FDebbie Roche fears that forcing people
OL,16,Fto keeping personal details, such as
OL,17,Fdriving licences and national
OL,18,Finsurance numbers, on their phones
OL,19,Fcould expose them to further abuse and
OL,20,Fcontrolling behaviour.
