OL,3,CCampaigners fear digital ID scheme
OL,4,Ccould be used as 'weapon of abuse'
OL,6,F"Those little mobile phone devices can
OL,7,Fbecome an extra weapon of abuse,"
OL,8,FDebbie said.
OL,10,F"When you think of all that data that
OL,11,Fis on there, it can open you up to
OL,12,Ffinancial abuse, identity theft.
OL,14,F"Survivors have got enough to deal
OL,15,Fwith. You would want the mobile phone
OL,16,Fto be a place of security and safety,
OL,17,Fsomething that could be turned to in
OL,18,Fneed of help."
