OL,3,CCampaigners fear digital ID scheme
OL,4,Ccould be used as 'weapon of abuse'
OL,6,FDigital ID cards: What is the
OL,7,Fgovernment's plan and how will they
OL,8,Fwork?
OL,10,FThe Government says digital ID will
OL,11,Fmake it easier to apply for housing
OL,12,Fand childcare, to access benefits, and
OL,13,Fwill stop those with no right to be in
OL,14,Fthe country from finding work.
OL,16,FThe idea is still in the consultation
OL,17,Fphase. Debbie says that must include
OL,18,Fhearing from domestic abuse victims.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
