OL,3,CCampaigners fear digital ID scheme
OL,4,Ccould be used as 'weapon of abuse'
OL,6,F"People have found a way to keep
OL,7,Fattacking, harrassing, stalking,
OL,8,Fvictimising people and it is worse for
OL,9,Fdomestic abuse survivors," she said.
OL,10,F"Because out there, people still won't
OL,11,Faccept that it happens."
OL,13,FPlymouth's Labour MP, Luke Pollard,
OL,14,Fsaid: "I think digital ID will make
OL,15,Four society safer. It will make public
OL,16,Fservices more efficient, and it will
OL,17,Fbring government into the 21st century.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
