OL,3,CCampaigners fear digital ID scheme
OL,4,Ccould be used as 'weapon of abuse'
OL,6,F"But to do that, we have to take
OL,7,Fpeople with us. And that means
OL,8,Fcorrectly listening to concerns where
OL,9,Fthey exist and acting on them in the
OL,10,Flegislation that is to come."
OL,12,FRebecca Smith, Conservative MP for
OL,13,FSouth West Devon, said: "I think they
OL,14,Fare using something that is deeply
OL,15,Funpopular with the public, simply as a
OL,16,Fgimmick to show that they are trying
OL,17,Fto do something to bring illegal
OL,18,Fimmigration down.
